类 AylaHttpServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • fi.iki.elonen.NanoHTTPD
      • fi.iki.elonen.router.RouterNanoHTTPD
        • com.aylanetworks.aylasdk.lan.AylaHttpServer

  • public class AylaHttpServer
extends fi.iki.elonen.router.RouterNanoHTTPD
    The AylaHttpServer is used as part of the communication protocol with LAN mode devices. The server listens for events from devices and routes them to the appropriate LAN module.

        public static AylaHttpServer createDefault(AylaSessionManager sessionManager)
